children.subject: If you CAN phase 1 126/127 do it, but right now they're completely full & closed to undergrads.

history.content:
CS 100 will definitely be significant extra work without Data 8 (though, I'm not sure if your vast experience with Data Science may be a factor).

Also, pairing it up with 170 could be risky, depending on how you manage heavy workloads.

I have a lot of experience with data science (I'm also taking the Data Science Decal now, but haven't taken Data 8), so would CS 100 be a lot of work for me? Planning on taking it with 170/188/161. 

On a side note, would it be a good idea to phase 1 126/127 for next semester? I would prefer to take 170/100/126, but I'm not sure whether I should even consider 126/127 being expanded. 

Thanks in advance!
